title: Bug 121682 - Exception thrown when exporting data from table containing highlight/map
description: Exception is thrown when attempting to export data from the attached report.
OB: An exception is thrown when exporting data from a table that includes a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
SR:
To reproduce the issue, follow these steps:
1. Add a table to the report that includes a group, a highlight rule, and a map rule in the group row.
2. Preview the report.
3. Attempt to export the data.
